freenet.node.fcp
Class ClientRequest

java.lang.Object
  freenet.node.fcp.ClientRequest
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientGet, ClientPutBase
public abstract class ClientRequest
extends Object

A request process carried out by the node for an FCP client. Examples: ClientGet, ClientPut, MultiGet.
